name: Kanshaku tamanage Kantarou no Toukaidou Gojuusan-tsugi [NES]
description:
Kanshakudama Nage Kantarou no Toukaidou Gojuusan Tsugi is an action game. It came out on 03-07-1986. Most rawgers rated the game as "Recommended".
Kanshakudama Nage Kantarou no Toukaidou Gojuusan Tsugi is available on NES.
